  .p-contact__line__button
    .p-contact__line__button__item.is-higirimaruyamadai.is-active(
      data-module="tabSwitch"
      data-options={
        target: "higirimaruyamadai",
        other: ['besshokoumyouji']
      }
    )
      a(href="javascript:void(0)")
        |日限丸山台
